### OpenAPI 文件管理接口测试

@routerPrefix = market
@contentType = application/json
@openapiFileId = cf8307eb-2793-40be-b37c-9aa5db2d9b64

### 1. 上传 OpenAPI 文档 - JSON 格式
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{routerPrefix}}/openapi/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary
Authorization: {{token}}

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="openapi_yaml_file.yaml"
Content-Type: application/json

< ../data/openapi_yaml_file.yaml

### 2. 上传子 OpenAPI 文档 - YAML 格式
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{routerPrefix}}/openapi/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary
Authorization: {{token}}

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="openapi_yaml_file.yaml"
Content-Type: application/yaml

< ../data/openapi_yaml_file.yaml

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="baseOpenapiFileID"

{{openapiFileId}}
--WebAppBoundary--

### 3. 获取 OpenAPI 文档列表 - 带分页和过滤
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{routerPrefix}}/openapi/files?page=1&pageSize=10
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{token}}

### 5. 获取 OpenAPI 文档内容
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{routerPrefix}}/openapi/content?openapiFileId={{openapiFileId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{token}}

### 8. 编辑 OpenAPI 文档
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{routerPrefix}}/openapi/edit
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "openapiFileId": "{{openapiFileId}}",
  "content": "{\n  \"openapi\": \"3.0.0\",\n  \"info\": {\n    \"title\": \"Updated PetStore API\",\n    \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n    \"description\": \"This is an updated OpenAPI specification\"\n  },\n  \"paths\": {\n    \"/pets\": {\n      \"get\": {\n        \"summary\": \"List all pets\",\n        \"responses\": {\n          \"200\": {\n            \"description\": \"Successful response\"\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}"
}

### 9. 下载 OpenAPI 文档
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{routerPrefix}}/openapi/download/{{openapiFileId}}
Authorization: {{token}}

### 10. 删除 OpenAPI 文档
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{routerPrefix}}/openapi/files/{{openapiFileId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{token}}